            "label": "Deploy etcd Quorum Cluster HA node",
            "command": "set -euo pipefail\nlog() { printf '[etcd_quorum_cluster_ha] %s\\n' \"$*\"; }\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/etcd_quorum_cluster_ha/compose.yml pull\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/etcd_quorum_cluster_ha/compose.yml up -d\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/etcd_quorum_cluster_ha/compose.yml ps\n      log \"node deployment complete\"\n",
            "sudo": true
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "node_step_4",
          "type": "configCommandNode",
          "position": {
            "x": 885,
            "y": 4815
          },
          "data": {
            "label": "Document etcd Quorum Cluster HA topology",
            "command": "set -euo pipefail\ncat >/tmp/etcd_quorum_cluster_ha-topology.md <<'EOF'\n# etcd Quorum Cluster HA\n\nMembers:\n- etcd-01: 10.0.160.11 (etcd)\n- etcd-02: 10.0.160.12 (etcd)\n- etcd-03: 10.0.160.13 (etcd)\n\nThree etcd members form an odd-number quorum with generated peer and client advertise URLs.\nEOF\ncat /tmp/etcd_quorum_cluster_ha-topology.md\n",
            "sudo": true
          }
        },
